snippet.title: Tap to Dive – Trailer
snippet.description:
A simple tilt-and-tap game.

http://www.taptodive.com
https://www.facebook.com/taptodive
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tap-to-dive/id980963853?mt=8

* Tilt to turn, tap to dive.
* Dive as deep as you can.
* Pick up bubbles to stay alive.
* Avoid the dangers of the sea.
* Collect coins to unlock characters and locations.

—

"Music: Jazzy Frenchy - Bensound.com"
